    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Circulation, transmission and exchange of knowledge, views and theories between countries, regions and people from different cultures by means of contact and encounter and how this has (mutual) impact on the cultural and artistic production.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
